{"tid":471053,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"1571 信邦集團 半新股","createTime":"2017-11-17T01:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T03:08:16.000Z","uid":46313,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d9284d660039aab51882ec7618bca2304ac37b91","tid":471053,"uid":46313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T01:57:02.000Z","msg":"有無人留意呢隻股票<br />\n<br />\n信邦是中國第二大供應商及最大型的汽車塑膠電鍍零件出口商。<br />\n<br />\n公司2016年底的借貸金額僅500萬元人民幣，處於淨現金狀態。<br />\n<br />\n國際市場的穩定發展，對於中國汽車內飾零件製造的龍頭企業來說，着實是很好的業績增長動力。事實上，信邦的業務毛利率表現出色，也得益於其產品質量受國際客戶的認同。信邦的毛利率於2016年達到41.1%，高於同行平均水平。<br />\n<br />\n值得留意的是，信邦的基石投資者是大名鼎鼎的雄牛資本(Bull Capital)，也是一個值得關注的亮點。"},{"pid":"713699ef95e6a554d2636f22ce7d796d4a6d1358","tid":471053,"uid":33338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:00:33.000Z","msg":"呢隻野遲下入埋港股通都唔奇"},{"pid":"2f7424e8aa49cc71e0228512e26ac1d8c2cd673d","tid":471053,"uid":46313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T05:24:50.000Z","msg":"岩岩買入左啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc85a3fed5124d3646736067bc245c47a3d981d9","tid":471053,"uid":29975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T09:20:49.000Z","msg":"基本面靚到癲 不過要等下<br />\n今日入貨良機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568953d1b18efa3033206f950c3ff5c3bd745437","tid":471053,"uid":60556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T09:26:17.000Z","msg":"下星期入先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b1312ef756049e59c9e42b2de6f7761c26b6433","tid":471053,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T10:28:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢隻野遲下入埋港股通都唔奇</blockquote><br />\n要平均市值50億一年內"},{"pid":"04189dbba034607066c2b4e16ff685829f6fe9af","tid":471053,"uid":46313,"li